This infographic presents the concept of digital literacy in a structured and visually engaging manner. It highlights the importance of using digital tools effectively and responsibly, along with key skills such as searching, evaluating, and communicating online. The design is divided into five sections, covering safe internet practices, useful digital tools, professional online presence, and communication habits. Each section uses clear icons, colors, and short bullet points to make the information easy to understand. Overall, the infographic emphasizes how students can develop essential digital skills to stay safe, productive, and professional in the digital world.
